squad.Decision.rationale | hasValue | GOAT-KING's reframe: the close *'ready when you are. go or ask anything.'* is doing structural work — separator between *I see you* and *we begin*. Shortening it loses the seam. Pre-committing in writing to resist the deadline-pressure temptation to compress.
